                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/johngreed/">约翰格利特</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-11-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">政府是人们在自然状态下同意产生的保护自身财产的形式；很好的自由政哲入门读物。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="776059886">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-776059886" class="vote-count">6</span>
